If that were true you wouldn't care what the law says.  Since you do not follow any moral system, and you don't fear the retribution of the law, then there is nothing holding you back from acting outside of its boundaries.  However, you do claim unwavering obedience to the law, and the only reason for doing so is retribution in the absence of morality, therefore you fear retribution of the law.<br>
